             was indicted for <rs id="t17931204-23-off130" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17931204-23-off130" type="offenceCategory" value="violentTheft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17931204-23-off130" type="offenceSubcategory" value="highwayRobbery"></interp>
               making an assault on the King's highway, on 
                     
                        <persName id="t17931204-23-victim313" type="victimName">
                           Edward 
                           Robinson
                        <interp inst="t17931204-23-victim313" type="surname" value="Robinson"></interp>
