                  , on the <rs id="t17931204-23-cd131" type="crimeDate">17th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17931204-23-off130 t17931204-23-cd131"></join>, putting him in fear and feloniously taking from his person, and against his will, eighteen shillings, the monies of the said 
                     <persName id="t17931204-23-person314">
                        Edward
                         Robinson
                     <interp inst="t17931204-23-person314" type="surname" value="Robinson"></interp>
